  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "DopCl75KukHPSGKMgjX+Azm+uzkDICrlUbhYHWQxZms=",
    "originContent": "Terminal molecular structure viewer — load, rotate, and explore proteins, nucleic acids, and small molecules from PDB/CIF files right in your terminal. No browser, no GUI, no dependencies.",
    "translatedContent": "ターミナル分子構造ビューア — PDB/CIFファイルからタンパク質、核酸、小分子を読み込み、回転し、ターミナル上で探検可能。ブラウザ不要、GUI不要、依存関係なし。"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "nrVeE3oDH0tNFm9CX5stkYPKAaCrnePTkJZtrLHmoDg=",
    "originContent": "## Features",
    "translatedContent": "## 特徴"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "dNDgmUzRtI56xGWM1kMNHXgwqiI46dRawvnBYfPMGeA=",
    "originContent": "- **3-tier render modes** — Braille, HD, and FullHD (Sixel/Kitty) with automatic SSH detection",
    "translatedContent": "- **3段階のレンダーモード** — ブレイル、HD、FullHD（Sixel/Kitty）と自動SSH検出"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "aN87A2OtMBaq1feSAyJjesSylBnCZpKdmO0DXL0xdFw=",
    "originContent": "- **PNG-compressed Kitty protocol** — ~10-20x smaller than raw RGBA, making FullHD viable over SSH",
    "translatedContent": "- **PNG圧縮Kittyプロトコル** — 生のRGBAより約10〜20倍小さく、SSH経由でのFullHDを実現"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "BAc4Ar5nxj1a9R/hY0Gtfv/cO8whzQN1wHbRjVjjpzI=",
    "originContent": "- **Cartoon ribbon visualization** — Lambert-shaded ribbons with depth fog for helices, sheets, and coils",
    "translatedContent": "- **カートンリボン表示** — ランバート陰影付きリボン、ヘリックス・シート・コイルに深度フォグ"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "JXKBynqbUBTuLVqLg8vDI9FtkYgidPMdLQ4SDczzv2g=",
    "originContent": "- **RNA/DNA support** — backbone, wireframe, and cartoon modes with base-type coloring",
    "translatedContent": "- **RNA/DNA対応** — バックボーン、ワイヤーフレーム、カートンモード、塩基タイプ別着色"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "wfqAPONxyw69b6jjWauip5lDoi1itR1gLhhuRMkKt28=",
    "originContent": "- **Small molecule rendering** — ligands as ball-and-stick, ions as spheres",
    "translatedContent": "- **小分子レンダリング** — リガンドはボール＆スティック、イオンは球体として表示"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "cvv/9FxW50fADjjSRDkQ681wr6sNBVNGEAAVSgXBq9k=",
    "originContent": "- **Interface analysis** — inter-chain contacts, binding pockets, and interaction visualization (H-bonds, salt bridges, hydrophobic contacts)",
    "translatedContent": "- **インターフェース解析** — 鎖間接触、結合ポケット、相互作用の可視化（H結合、塩橋、疎水性接触）"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "6vpDBQzPk4r2xToP3xwv1XMAKjrnj7mCA8uJqXJBYMk=",
    "originContent": "- **7 color schemes** — structure, chain, element (CPK), B-factor, rainbow, pLDDT (AlphaFold)",
    "translatedContent": "- **7種類のカラースキーム** — 構造、鎖、元素（CPK）、B因子、虹色、pLDDT（AlphaFold）"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "+Q07+G8ZKhNb3Mo7NGNZ/heFMxYIqOKwn5EGcxCy2dk=",
    "originContent": "- **Interactive controls** — vim-style rotation, zoom, pan with auto-rotation",
    "translatedContent": "- **インタラクティブ操作** — vim風回転、ズーム、パン、自動回転"
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "K0z1vVWdAEfqebFw4Y/oBnuWl73ZtalGHVAN3C8x0YE=",
    "originContent": "- **PDB & mmCIF** — both formats supported, with RCSB PDB fetch (`--fetch`)",
    "translatedContent": "- **PDB & mmCIF対応** — 両フォーマット対応、RCSB PDB取得機能（`--fetch`）"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "MKE+US1IIXZfitQeWNm9/Svz9Ih8rxO051wtB4aKFiU=",
    "originContent": "- **Single static binary** — zero runtime dependencies",
    "translatedContent": "- **単一の静的バイナリ** — 実行時依存関係ゼロ"
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
